{"tid":1527154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］添馬公園要人！","createTime":"2019-09-01T09:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:19:03.000Z","uid":203845,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f077bb797a0721ecd4d61e9c4048792c804b9168","tid":1527154,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"原來聽日同後日有罷工<br />\n學生亦都會罷課，大家一齊嚮應三罷<br />\n<br />\n琴日太子恐怖分子襲擊完市民後<br />\n應該會有更多人嚮應罷工<br />\n黨鐘亦都有更合理嘅籍口比人清算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全能嘅連登仔，我希望大家可以一齊三罷<br />\n唔單止罷，係要最大規模嘅癱瘓</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔喺機場嘅手足，一齊做文宣，推上去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月2 9月3 全民三罷 癱瘓香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bFG4TE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bFG4TE.jpg&h=fafcd574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4fK8KTG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4fK8KTG.jpg&h=f036e48a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1bc55c845afa6be154fc8f1b2f6c8bb6e7d2cf9","tid":1527154,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"601d26c096898326e27f6dbfca4b3505c562171f","tid":1527154,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"3fff1e79a615218d057296b95ca7cdc6792421c1","tid":1527154,"uid":35262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72866adb614fc063467fef828d81ef8961d5878c","tid":1527154,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 共同救港"},{"pid":"f2c29c69f8938446149a9f122b17b6d754250cdf","tid":1527154,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fff1e79a615218d057296b95ca7cdc6792421c1","tid":1527154,"uid":35262,"like":0,"dislike